{"data":{"page":{"id":"37a1da97-47fd-56a9-8478-d5ea9df1188c","html":"<p>大家好, 这是我的 Blog. 我在高一时就有过写 Blog 的想法, 但心有余而力不足. 那是我第一次接触网络开发, 已经有四个年头了, 今天重新拾起当初的想法, 希望能继续当年的梦想, 在这里和大家分享一些有意思的内容.</p>\n<!-- Hi, I'm Yujie, this is my blog. I bought this domain name a few years ago, planed to write build a personal website but left unattended. This domain was my first attempt to the internet and it is reborn to its new mission, share. -->\n<!-- That was my first attempt to write a website, I chosed wordpress as CMS but its awful performance makes everything tough. -->\n<!-- Recently, I found it's tiring to count for likes on wechat posts so decide to rejoin the freedom of internet and start a new space to write and share. -->\n<h3>Education</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>高中: Alevel 4A* 毕业于领科教育上海</li>\n<li>大学: Imperial College London Electronic and Information Engineering 大一在读</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Coding Experience</h3>\n<p>我在2018年独立开发了 Pastpaper Online 微信小程序, 2019年大约有30%的中国CIE考生使用 (25k用户). 前期主要使用微信小程序的原生语言, 后期觉得代码管理过于庞杂就转栈 React. 在使用 SaaS 服务前一直自己捣腾后端, 尝试过诸如 docker, Kuber 一类的技术, 不过只是菜鸟级别.</p>\n<!-- ### Features:\n\n* Easy editable content in **Markdown** files (posts, pages and parts)\n* **CSS** with `styled-jsx` and `PostCSS`\n* **SEO** (sitemap generation, robot.txt, meta and OpenGraph Tags)\n* **Social** sharing (Twitter, Facebook, Google, LinkedIn)\n* **Comments** (Facebook)\n* **Images** lazy loading and `webp` support (gatsby-image)\n* Post **categories** (category based post list)\n* Full text **searching** (Algolia)\n* **Contact** form (Netlify form handling)\n* **RSS** feed\n* 100% **PWA** (manifest.webmanifest, offline support, favicons)\n* Google **Analytics**\n* App **favicons** generator (node script)\n* Easy customizable base **styles** via `theme` object generated from `yaml` file (fonts, colors, sizes)\n* React **v.16** (gatsby-plugin-react-next)\n* **Components** lazy loading (social sharing)\n* **ESLint** (google config)\n* **Prettier** code styling\n* Webpack `BundleAnalyzerPlugin` -->","frontmatter":{"title":"About"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/about/","source":"pages"}}